trans-unit.source: Contains filter criteria for data extracted from a workflow instance in a <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions" />.
trans-unit.target: Contém os critérios de filtro para dados extraídos de uma instância de fluxo de trabalho em um <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue> specifies the value of a piece of data extracted from a workflow.
trans-unit.target: Um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue> Especifica o valor de uma parte dos dados extraídos de um fluxo de trabalho.

trans-unit.source: It is used to constrain the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> in a query of the tracking data base used by a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.
trans-unit.target: Ele é usado para restringir o conjunto de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objetos retornados pelo <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> em uma consulta de base de dados de rastreamento usada por um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingService>.

trans-unit.source: You can add <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue> objects to <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> to specify that the set of <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objects returned by <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> be constrained to those possessing the specified set of extracted data.
trans-unit.target: Você pode adicionar <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue> objetos <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQueryOptions.TrackingDataItems%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> para especificar que o conjunto de <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingWorkflowInstance> objetos retornados pelo <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.SqlTrackingQuery.GetWorkflows%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> ser restrita àqueles que possui o conjunto de dados extraídos especificado.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue" />.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue" /> class.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue" />.

trans-unit.source: The default constructor initializes <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> to a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: O construtor padrão inicializa <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A> como uma referência nula (`Nothing` no Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: You must set all of these properties in order to configure the <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.
trans-unit.target: Você deve definir todas essas propriedades para configurar o <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue>.

trans-unit.source: The qualified name of the activity from which the data was extracted.
trans-unit.target: O nome qualificado da atividade da qual os dados foram extraídos.

trans-unit.source: The name of the member from which the data was extracted.
trans-unit.target: O nome do membro da qual os dados foram extraídos.

trans-unit.source: A <see langword="string" /> representation of the value of the data.
trans-unit.target: A representação <see langword="string" /> do valor dos dados.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue" /> class by using the specified qualified name of an activity, data field name, and <see langword="string" /> representation of a data value.
trans-unit.target: Inicializa uma nova instância da classe <see cref="T:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue" /> usando o nome qualificado especificado de uma atividade, nome de campo de dados e representação <see langword="string" /> de um valor de dados.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, and <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> properties are set according to the values specified by the equivalent parameters to the constructor.
trans-unit.target: O <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.QualifiedName%2A>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A>, e <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.DataValue%2A> propriedades são definidas de acordo com os valores especificados pelos parâmetros equivalentes para o construtor.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> corresponds to the name specified in a <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> corresponde ao nome especificado em um <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> can, therefore, be set to specify an activity field or property; a member of an activity field or property; or a single element of an activity field or property (or a member of either) that implements the <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItemValue.FieldName%2A> Portanto, pode ser definido para especificar um campo de atividade ou a propriedade; um membro de um campo de atividade ou a propriedade; ou um único elemento de um campo de atividade ou propriedade (ou um membro da) que implementa o <xref:System.Collections.IEnumerable> interface.

trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingDataItem.FieldName%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.TrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>, <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.ActivityDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType> ou <xref:System.Workflow.Runtime.Tracking.WorkflowDataTrackingExtract.Member%2A?displayProperty=nameWithType>.
